title: Roky Erickson Live Oslo 2007
description:
Roky Erickson and The Explosives at Oeya Festival, Oslo, Norway 2007. This was recorded from web tv- so the quality is excellent.

And even if Roky's voice start to crack at the end, this show's worth watching. We're talking real legend here. This guy's probably fought more demons than Phil Spector, Brian Wilson and Syd Barret all together..

And just for those die hard fans- check out his current girlfriend backstage. Isn't she the very same he was married to in the sixties (if you've seen "You're gonna miss me", you'll know who I'm refering to..)


And people..Please help seed. It's kinda hard to upload new stuff regularly when you're stuck as the only seeder every time. Also,- I seed 24-7 as long as it takes.


Anyway.. Enjoy!
